window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ryan and his team have reached the capital.</b></p> <p>Fighting incursions is bad enough, but the many layers of political in-fighting just make him sick.</p> <p>Fortunately, his power is growing, and he's learning to forge his own path. To find the way forward though, he's going to have to learn the truth about his past.</p> <p>Join Ryan, Elu, Kumo, and Lian as they stand up to the heavens and the politics of men alike.</p>"; 
